WallpaperSize
March 2, 2021
WallpaperSize: Fix, Resize, Scale, Rotate Wallpapers
When you try to use a photo as wallpaper on home screen, you have no control in photo size? You are having problem to fit the full photo as background? The picture is zoomed-in and never let you resize to fit the screen? This app solves your problem.
Resize your wallpaper to fit the full screen of iPhone with WallpaperSize!!
WallpaperSize allows you to resize, rotate, and move your photo to perfectly fit the home screen. It automatically saves the image as a wallpaper in a specific size for you device!
Download on App Store
